title: To Clasp
author: Tinie_Snipah
pages:
#- Dear Clasp,
I am writing to appologise for my clear lack of dedication to a trade. I am sorry that I did not follow up on my offer within the time period I gave, and as such I believe the goods I delivered are not worth what you are paying.
#- I am lowering the payment due from 120i+2d to 104i+2d, meaning you are getting a 16i discount on the 108 stacks of sand I delivered to your home in Nine.
I hope that my actions will not sway you away from further trade.
Yours Truly
Tinie_Snipah
#- 